{
  "page": "House Shett",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>There are two branches of <b>House Shett</b> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a>:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower\" title=\"House Shett of Gull Tower\"><img alt=\"House Shett of Gull Tower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e2/House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower.svg/16px-House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e2/House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower.svg/24px-House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e2/House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower.svg/32px-House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower\" title=\"House Shett of Gull Tower\">House Shett of Gull Tower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Shett of Gulltown\"><img alt=\"House Shett of Gulltown.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg/16px-House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg/24px-House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg/32px-House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Shett of Gulltown\">House Shett of Gulltown</a></li></ul>\n<p>It is unknown which is the original line of House Shett, once holding the title of <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_True_Men\" title=\"King of the True Men\">King of the True Men</a> and ruling the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a>, and which is the cadet branch. Currently both branches are described as houses of <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knights</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Shett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The kings' line of the Shetts may be <a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gull_Tower\" title=\"House Shett of Gull Tower\">House Shett of Gull Tower</a>, since they blazon their arms with golden wings, a color commonly associated with royalty, and reside in Gull Tower, a seat separated from the other noble families of <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a>, including the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Shett of Gulltown\">other branch of House Shett</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:HousesVale\" title=\"Template:HousesVale\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:HousesVale&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:HousesVale (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li